    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with tons of love? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in really solid shape and runs like an absolute dream. It\u2019s been my trusty companion on so many trips, but it\u2019s finally time for it to find a new home. It\u2019s super clean, comfy, and honestly just a blast to drive. I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have\u2014it's totally ready for your next big adventure! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
