    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 Coupe featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This driver-focused example is equipped with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The mechanical integrity is excellent, with documented service on the dual-VANOS system and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe\u2014addressing the primary weak points of the E46 chassis. The suspension geometry remains precise with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the car tracks true under heavy lateral loads. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed-in for immediate performance use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Reliable daily driver. Minor cosmetic wear. Engine runs strong. Maintenance records included. Clean title.",
