    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily reliability and premium comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger bumper\u2014standard signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with the leather upholstery showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is rock solid; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes were serviced just 3,000 miles ago. It sits on a set of premium tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a dependable, well-documented vehicle ready for its next owner. Full service records are available for review.",
      "price": 31500.0,
