    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for this beauty! It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, with just the usual minor wear you'd expect from a car that's been enjoyed. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make its next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
